FBIS4-39975 "drsov113_b_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-113 Daily Report 11 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Intelligence, Counterintelligence Services Reunite Intelligence, Counterintelligence Services Reunite LD1106123694 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1100 GMT 11 Jun 94 LD1106123694 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] Russia's intelligence and counterintelligence services have reunited their work. This was confirmed by Sergey Stepashin today. However, he did not specify whether or not the Federal Counterintelligence Service and Yevgeniy Primakov's service [the Russian Foreign Intelligence Service of which Primakov is director] would be merging organizationally.
